<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>404 에러 - 페이지를 찾을 수 없음</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f3f3f3;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      }

      .error-code {
        font-size: 120px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
      }

      .error-message {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #555;
      }

      .back-button {
        margin-top: 30px;
      }

      .back-button a {
        text-decoration: none;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
      }

      .back-button a:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="error-code">404</div>
      <div class="error-message">페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.</div>
      <div class="back-button">
        <a href="/">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
